      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "1. Add a binary feature 'is_morning' to indicate if the departure time is between 6 AM and 12 PM.\n2. Create a 'weather_severity' feature that maps weather conditions to a severity score (e.g., Clear = 0, Storm = 3, Fog = 2).\n3. Introduce a 'day_of_week' feature to capture the day of the week from the departure time.\n4. Add a 'flight_duration' feature by calculating the difference between departure and arrival times (assuming arrival times are available in the dataset).\n5. Create a 'delay_cause' feature that maps delay_reason_code to a categorical representation (e.g., weather = 1, technical = 2, etc.).\n6. Add a 'is_weekend' feature to indicate if the departure time falls on a weekend.\n7. Introduce a 'is_peak_hour' feature to indicate if the departure time falls within peak travel hours (e.g., 7 AM - 9 AM and 5 PM - 7 PM).\n\nBy adding these features, we can capture more information that may be relevant to predicting flight delays, potentially improving the F1-score on the validation set.",
